title:
==============================
Project Garage Zero:
The Apprentice's Dilemma
==============================
STORY:
You are a young, bright-eyed individual, striving to become the next DevOps Engineer at MSM. You have just left your interview...
...and you can't remember where you parked your car!
You have a validated ticket but there's limited time before you have to pay extra for parking.
OBJECTIVE:
Find your car and leave the garage without paying an additional fee.
HOW TO WIN:
Locate your car and reach the garage exit before the step counter runs out.
